objectives: 1   Objectives of zone•  To provide a range of small-scale retail, business and community uses that serve the needs of people who live or work in the surrounding neighbourhood.•  To encourage mixed use developments to present an active frontage to the street by locating business, retail and community uses at ground level.•  To minimise conflict between land uses within the zone and land uses within adjoining zones.•  To enable other land uses that are complementary to and do not detract from the viability of retail, business and community uses within the zone.•  To encourage a safe, attractive, accessible and efficient pedestrian environment.
